data.description: Discover the charm of this cozy 3-bed/2-bath traditional home in the serene country living of New Caney. This thoughtfully designed residence features an open-concept layout, a spacious living area with abundant natural light pouring through large windows, and a chef's kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, natural gas, and a convenient island. The primary suite offers a generous sleeping area, a separate shower and tub, dual sinks, and ample closet space. Two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for a home office or guest accommodations. The outdoor space is a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch to create your oasis. Enjoy modern conveniences like smart home features, central air conditioning, and a two-car garage. Situated just minutes from 59 with easy access to the Grand Parkway(99), this home is in proximity to The Valley Ranch Town Center, offering Award-Winning Eateries, Live Music, Local Shops, and Family Fun. Welcome to your new haven!
